{"title_page": "Death Bed", "text_new": "{{short description|2019 single by Powfu featuring Beabadoobee}}\n{{Other uses|Deathbed (disambiguation){{!}}Deathbed}}\n{{Infobox song\n| name       = Death Bed\n| type       = single\n| cover      = Powfu - Death Bed.png\n| alt        =\n| artist     = [[Powfu]] featuring [[Beabadoobee]]\n| album      =\n| format     =\n* [[Music download|Digital download]]\n* [[Streaming media|streaming]]\n| recorded   = 2019\n| released   = <!-- Commercial release date, not SoundCloud upload date -->{{start date|2020|02|08|mf=y}}\n| genre      = \n* [[Hip hop music|Hip hop]]\n* [[lo-fi hip hop]]\n| length     = {{duration|m=2|s=53}}\n| label      = [[Columbia Records|Columbia]]\n| writer     =\n* [[Powfu|Isaiah Faber]]\n* [[Beabadoobee|Beatrice Laus]]\n* Oscar Lang\n| producer   = Otterpop\n| chronology = \n| prev_title = \n| prev_year  = \n| next_title =\n| next_year  =\n| misc       = {{External music video|{{YouTube|jJPMnTXl63E|\"Death Bed\"}}}}\n}}\n\"'''Death Bed'''\", released in later versions as \"'''Death Bed (Coffee for Your Head)'''\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/track/7eJMfftS33KTjuF7lTsMCx|title=\"death bed (coffee for your head) (feat. beabadoobee)\" on Spotify}}</ref> (stylized in [[Letter case#All lowercase|all lowercase]]) is a song by Canadian rapper [[Powfu]], featuring Filipino-British singer-songwriter [[Beabadoobee]]. Following Powfu signing to [[Columbia Records]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://genius.com/a/powfu-breaks-down-the-meaning-of-death-bed|title=Powfu Breaks Down The Meaning Of \"Death Bed\"|website=[[Genius (website)|Genius]]|last=Reneau|first=Steven|date=March 6, 2020|accessdate=March 18, 2020}}</ref> the song was released on streaming services on February 8, 2020, after initially being uploaded to [[SoundCloud]] in 2019. The song samples 2017 song \"Coffee\" by Beabadoobee, whom is also credited as a feature.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://headlineplanet.com/home/2020/03/08/powfu-beabadoobees-death-bed-picks-up-pop-radio-airplay-reaches-50-million-spotify-streams/|title=Powfu & Beabadoobee's \"Death Bed\" Picks Up Pop Radio Airplay, Reaches 50 Million Spotify Streams|website=Headline Planet|last=Cantor|first=Brian|date=March 8, 2020|accessdate=March 18, 2020}}</ref>\n\nThe song went viral on the video sharing app [[TikTok]] in early 2020.<ref name=\"Genius BG\">{{cite web|url=https://genius.com/a/powfu-s-death-bed-samples-beabadoobee-s-coffee|title=Powfu's Viral Hit \"Death Bed\" Arrives On Streaming Services After Lengthy Sample Clearance Delay|website=Genius|last=Fu|first=Eddie|date=February 13, 2020|accessdate=March 18, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Background==\nThe song's commercial release was delayed by a year due to the clearance of the [[Sampling (music)|sample]] of Beabadoobee's 2017 song \"Coffee\". Powfu said on [[Twitter]] in April 2019 that he had not put it on [[Spotify]] because he was \"scared [he'd] get in trouble from the sample [he] use[s] in it\", but said he \"would upload it anyway\" and told his followers to give him \"a week and a half\". It was finally released to streaming and download services in February 2020.<ref name=\"Genius BG\"/>\n\n==Composition==\nColumbia's British subsidiary [[Sony Music UK]] described it as a \"lo-fi hip hop single\".<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pressparty.com/pg/newsdesk/sonymusicuk/view/205330/|title=Powfu \u2013 New Single 'Death Bed' Feat Beabadoobee Out Now|publisher=[[Sony Music UK]]|via=[[Pressparty]]|date=March 2, 2020|accessdate=March 18, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Australia ([[ARIA Charts|ARIA]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/singles-chart|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 Singles|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|date=April 6, 2020|accessdate=April 4, 2020}}</ref>\n| 6\n|-\n{{single chart|Austria|16|artist=Powfu|song=Death Bed|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 2, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Flanders|34|artist=Powfu feat. Beabadoobee|song=Death Bed|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 10, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Wallonia|46|artist=Powfu feat. Beabadoobee|song=Death Bed|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 4, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Canada|20|artist=Beabadoobee|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 8, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Czechdigital|17|year=2020|week=14|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 7, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Denmark ([[Tracklisten]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hitlisten.nu/default.asp?w=13&y=2020&list=t40|title=Track Top-40 Uge 13, 2020|publisher=[[Hitlisten]]|accessdate=April 8, 2020}}</ref>\n| 10\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Estonia ([[Eesti Tipp-40]])<ref name=\"estonianchart\">{{Cite web|url=https://ekspress.delfi.ee/areen/eesti-tipp-40-muusikas-selle-nadala-kangelased-on-the-weeknd-ja-ag?id=89401195|title=Eesti Tipp-40 Muusikas: Selle n\u00e4dala kangelased on The Weeknd ja AG|language=Estonian|last=Nestor|first=Siim|website=[[Eesti Ekspress]]|date=March 31, 2020|accessdate=April 9, 2020}}</ref>\n| 9\n|-\n{{single chart|Finland|9|artist=Powfu feat. Beabadoobee|song=Death Bed|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 23, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| France ([[Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique|SNEP]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://snepmusique.com/les-tops/le-top-de-la-semaine/top-albums/?semaine=14?&annee=2020&categorie=Top%20Singles|title=Top Singles (Week 14, 2020)|publisher=[[Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique]]|language=French|accessdate=April 7, 2020}}</ref>\n| 31\n|-\n{{single chart|Germany2|20|songid=1954287|artist=Powfu feat. Beabadoobee|song=Death Bed|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 9, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Hungarystream|15|year=2020|week=14|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 102, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Ireland4|13|date=20200327|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 28, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Italy ([[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana|FIMI]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fimi.it/top-of-the-music/classifiche.kl#/charts/3/2020/13|title=Top Singoli \u2013 Classifica settimanale WK 13|publisher=[[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana]]|language=Italian|accessdate=March 28, 2020}}</ref>\n| 19\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Malaysia ([[Recording Industry Association of Malaysia|RIM]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/RecordingIndustryMalaysia/photos/pcb.3357908454236501/3357908324236514/?type=3&theater|title=Top 20 Most Streamed International & Domestic Singles In Malaysia|work=[[Recording Industry Association of Malaysia]]|publisher=Recording Industry Association of Malaysia|accessdate=April 5, 2020}}</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n{{single chart|Dutch100|42|artist=Powfu feat. Beabadoobee|song=Death Bed|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 10, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| New Zealand ([[Recorded Music NZ]])<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=4841|title=NZ Top 40 Singles Chart|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|date=April 6, 2020|accessdate=April 4, 2020}}</ref>\n| 7\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Norway ([[VG-lista]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vglista.no/topplister/topp-20-single-2020-12/|title=VG-lista \u2013 Topp 20 Single uke 12, 2020|publisher=[[VG-lista]]|accessdate=March 21, 2020}}</ref>\n| 14\n|-\n{{single chart|Portugal|21|artist=Powfu|song=Death Bed|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 9, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Scotland|41|date=20200403|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 4, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Singapore ([[Recording Industry Association (Singapore)|RIAS]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rias.org.sg/rias-top-charts/|title=RIAS International Top Charts Week 13|publisher=Recording Industry Association (Singapore)|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200403095609/https://www.rias.org.sg/rias-top-charts/|archive-date=April 3, 2020}}</ref>\n| 5\n|-\n{{single chart|Slovakdigital|28|year=2020|week=14|rowheader=true|accessdate=April 7, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Spa